resources.string: Given the OCR-extracted text from a machine reading, analyze the text to identify parameter names, values, and units(if available). Structure the output as a JSON object with the following format: { \'parameter_name\': { \'value\': <numeric_value>, \'unit\': \'<unit_if_available>\' } } \n Raw ocr: Pouer SPed TOraue 23 kW 58.6 RPM 389 kNe \n
